{"tid":2004604,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"余文樂歎居台灣，養尊處優變「谷德昭」","createTime":"2020-05-06T14:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T16:18:37.000Z","uid":215823,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"318c0c376e35faea619e0182cd9a0e5a30c43a0a","tid":2004604,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T14:15:03.000Z","msg":"余文樂曾經是潮人icon，3年前他與台灣「皮帶大王」千金王棠云結婚。現時已是一子之父的他，為照顧家庭長期留在台灣，全力打理潮牌生意。不過未知是否因為減少在幕前出現關係，在儀容外表上，近年余文樂變得隨意甚至有點不修篇幅，日前他貼出近照，就被網民嘲「臉容急速衰老」，樣子十足昔日脹爆的「谷德昭」。<br />\n<br />\n余文樂在IG動態貼出短片，片中他和老婆王棠云在車廂輕快地哼着歌，余文樂表情多多，老婆則兩手揈揈，表現興奮。片中只見余文樂正面望向鏡頭，圓面和IG所貼的側面相差甚遠，不但擺脫不了「谷德昭」的影子，濃濃的「大叔」feel更是無所遁形。雖然余文樂去年曾上載重肌相，並表示「好想再練回來」，不過要重拾當年型仔模樣，看來他仍需要下點功夫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4FX2z0B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4FX2z0B.png&h=69a2f723&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/05/06/221311_775f32073c2f923419ffd5c13773fbbd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F05%2F06%2F221311_775f32073c2f923419ffd5c13773fbbd.png&h=4a67326c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53d3006f4e036d03893cecaf434274d5259db9aa","tid":2004604,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T14:15:21.000Z","msg":"特朗普真係落台啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2004593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2004593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1c966615cd701388f10eab0f54ad177947deb7fa","tid":2004604,"uid":116530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T14:16:27.000Z","msg":"柒撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e72600b5b420caf0123182394a5f27e7593c76","tid":2004604,"uid":104804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T14:17:41.000Z","msg":"享受既台灣自由:支持中國"},{"pid":"1dcd24daa432b8f48e8046559d0858384e29fd30","tid":2004604,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime